@janniksin back-to-back @wimbledon title came with an exclusive @nike @acg reveal. Off court, the world No. 1 wore a custom Radical Airflow jacket, transforming Nike's viral hole-covered running T-shirt into breathable outerwear for the first time. @serenawilliams also wore a bespoke Radical Airflow tennis look during her Wimbledon return.⁠
⁠
The custom pieces spotlight the future of Nike ACG's innovation-focused direction. After the Radical Airflow T-shirt became one of the brand's standout launches this year, the perforated knit is already expanding into hats, with outerwear now making its debut through Sinner's one-off Wimbledon look.

