@kithtreats is embracing Japanese tea culture with its new Treats Matcha capsule, launching July 17. Inspired by the Japanese tea ceremony, the collection centers on three limited-edition swirls made with THE NODOKA's specially selected matcha, genmaicha, and hojicha, alongside a range of apparel and a collaborative matcha set with Fellow.⁠
⁠
The drop includes four signature T-shirt designs in men's and kids' sizing, plus the Kith for Fellow Matcha Set, a complete at-home kit featuring a ceramic bowl, whisk, whisk stand, spoon, and tea tray. The collection will be available at Kith Treats Tokyo, Kith Treats Osaka, and through Kith's online store and app in Japan.

