Paulina Porizkova (@paulinaporizkov) and Jeff Greenstein (@sjeffgreenstein) have officially tied the knot! The celebration took place in Italy on July 3, at the Villa Crespi in Orta San Giulio, following a romantic ceremony at a lakeside town hall. Their location was full circle, as Paulina had first visited Villa Crespi for a photoshoot 30 years prior, and returned with Jeff in 2024. “As we made our way through Germany and Switzerland to Italy, we had the same thought at the same time: ‘why don’t we swing by Villa Crespi and see if we can get married there,” shares Paulina. The rest was history. Tap the link in our bio for a look inside their Italian lakeside celebration.

